
Installing ZAP in Linux

Step 1 : Download zap from this offical website : https://www.zaproxy.org/download/
step 2 : Open your terminal Swtich to root and type cd Downloads 
step 3 : Now lets make it executable file by typing : chmod +x name_of_file_you_downloaded
step 4 : after making it a executable file now type : ./your_file_name

Its done!!
